    "description": "<p><strong>ADVANTECH</strong> is the world leader in Embedded & Applied Computing, eAutomation and Industrial & Network computing platforms. With a global presence and an extensive network of offices worldwide, we manufacture and integrate advanced industrial computing platforms and provide system expertise to system integrators for their solution needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In <strong>ADVANTECH</strong>, Our culture empowers our people to achieve their true potential and creativity. We believe in sharing success with our people and in listening to the many voices that work together to support our single vision. We are looking for aspiring talents to join our fast-growing and dynamic organization.</p>\r\n",
